data.text:
“Desamantey Matti Kadoi, Desamantey Manushuloi” – Gurajada Apparao

A nation is not made up of soil. It is made up of People. People like you, me and all of us. I have decided to voice my protest, my anger against those terrorists that have hit the very heart of MY BELOVED COUNTRY INDIA.

My heart goes out to each and every person who have put their life in front to get the hotsages back
